{"type": "article", "id": 29109, "title": "隐藏式灯具", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-04T22:55:17Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 88, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160704162805VvasidR47pB09uZz.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>第一次看到 Christian Torels 为 <a href=\"http://www.leklint.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">LE KLINT</a> 设计的 MUTATIO 台灯时，你或许还会纳闷这个漆黑的圆柱体把光源藏去了哪里。采用了隐藏式的设计，只有当你按下开关时 MUTATIO 的灯罩才会一点点打开，露出白色的内里，光线则随着开合角度变化以不同的明暗程度倾泻而出，本身就是一个调光器。除了台灯之外，MUTATIO 还有壁灯款，极简低调的造型可以成为你在夜读时的好伙伴。<a href=\"http://www.leklint.com/en-GB/Products/Show-Product/Categories-Table/LE-KLINT-353-MUTATIO.aspx?Product=PROD701\" rel=\"nofollow\">台灯</a>和<a href=\"http://www.leklint.com/en-GB/Products/Show-Product/Categories-Wall/LE-KLINT-353-MUTATIO-WALL.aspx?Product=PROD748\" rel=\"nofollow\">壁灯</a>的售价为分别 469 和 539 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607041630080RolGyZiSajw8ALC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704163008jUEmBR2rdyIHe8tC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607041630087kqKSJPcHB4tQobR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334816\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704163008DkTrUGWuSix2IYnv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.335000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}